Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:52.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:02:00.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所へいざ集わんと 導かれしは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:06.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}志携えて 立ち向かえ
