Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:59.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:50.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.43,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界将要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果注定难逃死灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟该相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:50.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.70,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必体会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:59.63,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}这撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.33,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}响彻在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的镇魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.71,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然从飘乎的现实中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.15,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找寻你的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.75,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.48,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.73,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.77,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因为曾经深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.53,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}残留的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.45,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:50.38,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Comment: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,=============STORY===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袋状结构破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测不到任何奇居子的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认融合个体䌷仍然存活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子刚才对我做了非常过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它们对我的朋友和同伴做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 希格斯粒子密度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 听话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科户濑机 严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇550的希格斯粒子密度急剧上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轨道在与䌷和科户濑机的接触点发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来人 去救䌷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 䌷她…！
Comment: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Comment: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.05,title,NTP,0,0,0,,愿 望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体整备班 至岐神开发厂区特殊培养槽集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船员医疗班 火速救治受伤的卫人操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重伤者送往高度紧急治疗室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻伤者送往医务局第三科或中央医院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 䌷她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在丧失了90%的身体组织
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把䌷恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前出击并回舰的机体中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前约有50%已完成整备并运回机库待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个融合个体又救了我们一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有她 我们肯定已经无家可归了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真是好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅和你都没事真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才打了那么场恶战啊 你就少计较点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 没想到你换成了义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是坚决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奶奶建议的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为组织再生要花很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手脚你很快就能适应的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还方便得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你挺精神的 我也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候可以出院？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说我了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷还没恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC99DCF&}给䌷姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}保护了希德尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H978FC9&}祝你能赶快好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢她的人有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之前好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转换炉管的第1024次定期清扫将按时进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次清扫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快点向䌷道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说战斗口粮换新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去试吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘移民舰是在放出先遣队后返航希德尼娅的途中遇袭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有人顺利到达七号行星就已经不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在大众合船正在逼近雷姆星系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很累的样子 估计是没怎么睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风他累了或者身体不舒服了也从来不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他的这一点很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也反而让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也认识一个和长道很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以常常很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看到他一个人承担太多东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是长道一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他一个人待一阵子 很快就会振作起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风长道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天也来看望䌷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷已经移到通常培养槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胞衣已经基本上完全复原 只等恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃相太难看了啦 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？星…白…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星 白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一不小心睡着了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷 谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 听说你醒了 我就把它带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我可以摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要温柔一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软软的 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.01,eyecatch,NTP,1020,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　无人小摊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.98,eyecatch,NTP,950,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　外周壁连接桥内部通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前希德尼娅与大众合船所在的位置之间隔着恒星雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们处于对方的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为按照计划进入雷姆星系 本舰将开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 继续保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在为外壳设置了专用的房间 让她在其中待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现有武器再加上䌷也还是敌不过大众合船的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长是另有妙计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过上一场战斗 融合个体反对派的势力已经大幅削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个东西怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就将进入第一次启动实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我转告由蕾博士 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 能看到外面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比之前的房间大了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢看书 所以小一点也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是觉得这里离居住区有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就一声不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我就是在刚才的䌷身上看到了一个人住在地下的她的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 去拜托缬让䌷能够进入居住区嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 进来一下说不定还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来现在重力就已经不稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发生事故怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别走那么快啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 从管理局那边拿到的地图上也是这么标的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又是这么黑漆漆的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我没事 赶紧往前走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅正面喷射口 已打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让工作队撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 行星九号的卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向喷射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布重力警报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅现在将开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将安全带扣在安全扶手上 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅现在将开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将安全带扣在安全扶手上 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道 刚才是不是有什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点了 再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向喷射 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面第一、第二喷射口 点火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种振动是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说起来今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷射已稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力场发生装置及平衡即将恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道 到外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是居住塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那整栋建筑里住着很多人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那里有好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多人 肯定也有很多种生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能变成人类的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去很多地方 结识很多人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该有多棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们每个人都知道你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没想过能亲眼见到这样的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的东西怎么会在走廊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,150,0,0,,{\an7}谷风长道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}今天是新训练生入住的日子，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}但是您的物品还未整理完毕。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}因此我们将其放到了门外。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}请见谅。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希德尼娅军总务科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不能再住宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不是在跟你说笑话啊 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比计划的要慢 所以我一直很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 义肢也需要调整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 有人来电了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 那我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长 长道 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 突然找你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能让我住一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.05,0:22:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶——？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
